# Code of Conduct

## 1. Purpose
We are committed to fostering a welcoming and inclusive environment for everyone. This Code of Conduct outlines our expectations for participants within our community.

## 2. Expected Behavior
- Be respectful and inclusive.
- Communicate openly and with empathy.
- Be considerate of different perspectives and experiences.
- Collaborate in a constructive and positive manner.

## 3. Unacceptable Behavior
- Harassment, discrimination, or offensive comments.
- Personal attacks, trolling, or disruptive behavior.
- Sharing inappropriate content.
- Any conduct that violates laws or ethical standards.

## 4. Reporting and Enforcement
If you experience or witness any violations, please report them to [contact-email@example.com].

Violations of the Code of Conduct may result in actions such as warnings, temporary suspension, or permanent removal from the community.

## 5. Acknowledgment
By participating in this community, you agree to abide by this Code of Conduct and contribute to a positive environment.

